1. On je negde *negde* izgubio svoju torbu. (He lost his bag somewhere.)
2. Negde *negde* u svetu postoji mesto koje je idealno za nas. (Somewhere in the world there is a place that is perfect for us.)
3. Mislim da je negde *negde* usput zaboravila svoj novčanik. (I think she forgot her wallet somewhere along the way.)
4. Nedavno sam negde *negde* čuo za neki događaj. (Recently I heard somewhere about some event.)
5. Negde *negde* u daljini bila je planina. (Somewhere in the distance was a mountain.)